OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777551071
OL,3,CPolice investigate assault claims at
OL,4,CSEND children's home
OL,6,FPolice are investigating allegations
OL,7,Fof residents being assaulted at a home
OL,8,Ffor children with special needs.
OL,10,FLincolnshire Police said it was
OL,11,Fcarrying out inquiries "relating to
OL,12,Fsome residents" at Acacia Hall,
OL,13,FFriesthorpe, near Market Rasen.
OL,15,FEducation watchdog Oftsted said the
OL,16,Fhome's registration had been suspended.
OL,18,FThe nearby Acacia School is unaffected
OL,19,Fand continuing to operate as normal.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
