OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777551071
OL,3,CPolice investigate assault claims at
OL,4,CSEND children's home
OL,6,FA Lincolnshire Police spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our inquiries are ongoing and
OL,8,Fwe continue to work with the local
OL,9,Fauthorities and the school as part of
OL,10,Four investigation.
OL,12,F"We've been made aware that Ofsted
OL,13,Fhave suspended the licence for the
OL,14,Fresidential facility."
OL,16,FAccording to the Acacia Hall website,
OL,17,Fthe home "offers residential provision
OL,18,Ffor neurodivergent children and young
OL,19,Fpeople, who have additional complex
OL,20,Flearning needs".
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@VO]
