PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777551071
OL,3,CPolice investigate assault claims at
OL,4,CSEND children's home
OL,6,FIts residents access Acacia School as
OL,7,Fday pupils along with children from
OL,8,Fother homes.
OL,10,FAn Ofsted spokesperson said: "We can
OL,11,Fconfirm that we have suspended the
OL,12,Fregistration of Acacia Hall.
OL,14,F"We are working closely with other
OL,15,Fagencies, including the police, as
OL,16,Fthey carry out their investigation.
OL,17,FWe're unable to comment any further at
OL,18,Fthis stage."
OL,26,@rD@^OUvD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
