FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777551071
OL,3,CPolice investigate assault claims at
OL,4,CSEND children's home
OL,6,FTara Jones, assistant director for
OL,7,Fchildren's safeguarding at
OL,8,FLincolnshire County Council, said:
OL,9,F"We're aware of Ofsted's decision to
OL,10,Fsuspend the registration of Acacia
OL,11,FHall, and we're supporting
OL,12,FLincolnshire Police with their
OL,13,Finvestigation into the concerns
OL,14,Fconnected to the home. We're unable to
OL,15,Fcomment further at this time as this
OL,16,Fremains a live investigation."
OL,18,FKisimul, which operates the home,
OL,19,Fdeclined to comment.
OL,26,@qD@AOUxD@^O]
